<p><strong>Large fiend (demon), chaotic evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 16 (natural armor)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 136 (13d10+65)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft.</p>

